		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="442" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfbf">(仅盾)<span color="#ffffff">坚盾重甲蟹使用</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">蟹壳烧</span><span color="#ffffff">的火元素力量，发射2-3枚火焰弹，均造成</span><span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffb299">(固有天赋)<span color="#ffffff">坚盾重甲蟹处于陆地上时，会打开元素护甲使用元素力，而进入水下则会暂时关闭护甲，保留关前盾量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="395" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfbf">(仅盾)<span color="#ffffff">坚盾重甲蟹用力起跳，重重下落，均造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">75%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="419" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffbf">(仅水下)<span color="#ffffff">坚盾重甲蟹蓄力，进行持续回旋，接触造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">100%,20%,5%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
