		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1164" width="436" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蟹壳烧：<span color="#ff9999">10.8火</span><span>盾，击破后将不会使用部分技能，不恢复。该状态下，抗打断0.7。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">坚盾重甲蟹进行左右抓划攻击，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
